modal.aadhaarConsentMessage:
We confirm that:
a) I/We have been given other alternative means by Bandhan Bank for KYC purposes including physical KYC by submitting officially valid documents and I/We have voluntarily chosen Aadhaar based KYC.
b) I/We am/are aware that my/our Information can be used only for any of the following purposes and not for any other purpose:
(i) for requirements as per KYC norms, PML Act, 2002 and rules thereunder and RBI guidelines;
(ii) for any other facility related to banking operations and services;
(iii) for carrying out authentication/offline verification by any other mode or facility as may be permitted from time to time under the applicable law;
c) I/We hereby authorise and provide consent to the Bank to collect, disclose, share, store, preserve and use the Information and authentication data and records, as may be required under the applicable law or for the purposes above. I/We have been explained in local language about the consent, purpose of collecting Aadhaar and the nature of information that may be shared upon authentication.
d) I/We confirm that the Information shared are true, correct, complete and pertain to me. I/We shall not hold Bandhan Bank or any of its officials responsible in case of any incorrect information provided by me/us.
